import re

def extract_package_info(long_description):
    info = {}
    info[''] = re.search("setup\\(name='(.*?)',", long_description).group(1)
    info['version'] = float(re.search('version=(.*?),', long_description).group(1))
    info['author'] = re.search("author='(.*?)',", long_description).group(1)
    info['author_email'] = re.search("author_email='(.*?)',", long_description).group(1)
    info['description'] = re.search("description='(.*?)'", long_description).group(1)
    return info
